# Environment: prod = the EXISTING zyl-elevator-prod (source of truth).
#
# DO NOT `terraform apply` here. The live prod network is owned by CloudFormation
# (stack ZeyalabsInfraSetUp) and its resources already exist; applying these
# modules would try to CREATE duplicates. This stack is a read-only reference.
#
# To stand up a NEW production-like stack, use environments/yecl-prod (project
# yecl-elevator) which builds a dedicated, non-colliding environment.
